//MAIL
  "Mail_RobinsRefusal": "Hey @!^^Sorry for my speedy exit from the Caverns... not my finest moment, I'll admit, but I draw the line at being haunted while I'm hammering!^^If you do want that building repaired though, I could still help. I have an old colleague in Zuzu City that I can contact for you; Carl's a great guy and is the next best carpenter for miles, so I can think of no-one better to help us out.^^I've already designed some blueprints for him follow and bundled the price with the material cost and his fees. Stop by anytime and purchase the blueprints if you'd like to begin the renovation work. Take care!  ^^   -Robin   ^   ^  P.S. Please accept these as a small apology! %item id (O)709 10 %%[#]An Apology From Robin",
  "Mail_CarlRecycling": "Hiya @!^^I really enjoyed working on ya lil' project in the Caverns! I cleared out loads'a old stuff, but I saved what I could for ya. Take it easy, Kiddo   ^   -Carl %item id (O)388 80 %%[#]A Gift From Carl",
  "Mail_BobsRepairs": "Hi @!^^Thanks again for all of the great materials. Sid and a few of the others from the Speakeasy agreed to help me; we worked throughout the whole night and I'm really happy with what we've done!^^Stop by the next time you're in the Caverns. See you soon!  ^^   -Bob   ^   ^  P.S. Sorry for the bad handwriting... controlling a pencil with telekinesis isn't as easy as I thought it'd be![#]Bob's Renovations",
  "Mail_SidsThanks": "@,^^I don't like you. While you're breathing you have no business whatsoever in my bar, however, I appreciate your kindness towards the kid, Bob.^^We've been trying to talk to him for over a century, but he unwittingly created a barrier around himself that we couldn't breach. Whatever you've done, it's worked. He dropped his defences enough that we were finally able to visit him last night.^^Don't think this will change my attitude towards you; I don't do business with breathers... but I'm grateful for what you've done.^^Take this, and NEVER speak of it. ^^   -Sid %item money 5500 %%[#]A Thanks From Sid",

//VANILLA NPCS
  "Dialogue_Demetrius.1": "Bioluminescence is a naturally occurring phenomenon.#$b#It's caused by a chemical reaction during metabolic processes in both plants and insects.",
  "Dialogue_Demetrius.2": "Did you know that the bioluminescence emitted from fungi is also known as 'Foxfire'?", 
  "Dialogue_Robin.1": "I've come to the firm conclusion that I'm an above-ground person.#$b#There's nothing better than the sun on your back as you work!$h",
  "Dialogue_Wizard.1": "The Caverns have awakened again and are brimming with old magics; both light and dark.#$b#Treat them with respect and they may yet reveal their secrets to you.",
  "Event_Demetrius.1": "Good morning @!#$b#I've just been to see how our cave experiment is coming along.#$b#I've got both good and bad news...#$b#The bad news is there's been some erosion inside the cave... I'm afraid one of the interior walls has partially collapsed.$s",
  "Event_Demetrius.2": "Luckily the damage is only superficial and the local species haven't been affected.#$b#The interesting news is that the collapse has created an opening into a vast cavernous network underneath your farm.", 
  "Event_Demetrius.3": "I've briefly looked inside; there's some very unusual fungi in there I'd like to study further when I have the chance!$u#$b#If you decide to venture in, please be carful...#$b#Robin wouldn't be very happy with me if anything were to happen you!$h",
  "Event_Robin.1": "Demetrius' insanity strikes again! Why he had to come down here I'll never know.$6",
  "Event_Robin.2": "Now, where did he say that abandoned building was?",
  "Event_Robin.3": "Aaaaaaaaaaaah!!",

//BOB
  "Bob.name": "Bob",

//BOB ANIMATION
  "Animation_Bob.Practice": "Mr. Rasmodius says that if I practice enough and improve my focus, one day I may be able to do more than just telekinesis.",
  "Animation_Bob.Reading": "%Bob is too engrossed in his book to notice you.",
  "Animation_Bob.Gaming": "%Bob is busy concentrating on his game; he looks very happy.",
  "Animation_Bob.Mourning": "%Today is the anniversary of the mine collapse. Bob is busy remembering his friends and family.",

//BOB GIFTS
  "Gifts_Bob.Love": "This is so thoughtful. I love it; thank you!$h",
  "Gifts_Bob.Like": "Ooooo! I'm sure I'll find a use for this, thanks!",
  "Gifts_Bob.Dislike": "You get that I'm a ghost, right?! I can't eat or drink!$u",
  "Gifts_Bob.Hate": "Ugh. What am I meant to do with this?! I guess I could throw it at the pit-fiends.$u",
  "Gifts_Bob.Neutral": "Thanks, that's really kind.",

//BOB MOVIES
  "Movie_Bob.Like.1": "I'm eager for the movie to start; I'm not sure how long I can manifest this outfit for.",
  "Movie_Bob.Like.2": "Bob is eagerly watching the screen.",
  "Movie_Bob.Like.3": "Moving pictures never cease to amaze me. Thanks for bringing me along.",
  "Movie_Bob.Documentary.1": "I've just read the movie poster; this looks like it's going to be really interesting!",
  "Movie_Bob.Documentary.2": "Bob is fascinated by the movie.",
  "Movie_Bob.Documentary.3": "I love learning new things about the world; I've missed so much!",
  "Movie_Bob.Action.1": "This movie sounds like it's going to be fun!", 
  "Movie_Bob.Action.2": "Bob hovers over the edge of his seat.",
  "Movie_Bob.Action.3": "That was fantastic! Thanks so much for inviting me.",
  "Movie_Bob.Horror.1": "I'm not convinced I'm going to enjoy this. I think you and I have very different ideas of horror.",
  "Movie_Bob.Horror.2": "Pfft! I've seen grave-snails cough up scarier things than this.",
  "Movie_Bob.Horror.3": "Hang on, I need to check if I've still got my soul; it may have departed out of sheer boredom.", 
  "Movie_Bob.Romance.1": "Please tell me we aren't watching a romance?!",
  "Movie_Bob.Romance.2": "Bobs makes a vomiting expression... which is amazing given his lack of mouth.",
  "Movie_Bob.Romance.3": "I thought over a century of standing alone in a desolate mine was the pinnacle of boredom... this movie proved me wrong!",

//BOB SPECIAL ORDER
  "SpecialOrder_Bob.Name": "A Revenant's Repairs",
  "SpecialOrder_Bob.Text": "I feel it's time to repair the Mineshaft and the old Miner's Hut in the Caverns, but I'm going to need some materials. I have plenty of stone, but need wood, hardwood and iron bars. Can you help me?                     -Bob",
  "SpecialOrder_Bob.Obj0": "Gather 50 pieces of hardwood",
  "SpecialOrder_Bob.Obj1": "Gather 350 pieces of wood",
  "SpecialOrder_Bob.Obj2": "Gather 20 iron bars",
  "SpecialOrder_Bob.Obj3": "Add the hardwood to the materials stockpile in the Forgotten Miner's Hut kitchen.",
  "SpecialOrder_Bob.Obj4": "Add the wood to the materials stockpile in the Forgotten Miner's Hut kitchen.",
  "SpecialOrder_Bob.Obj5": "Add the iron bars to the materials stockpile in the Forgotten Miner's Hut kitchen.",

//BOB DIALOGUE
  "Dialogue_Bob.Boots": "$query PLAYER_HAS_SEEN_EVENT Host {{ModId}}_EventBobHeart2#Did... did you steal my boots?!$u#$b#Meh. As I'm rocking the 'bedsheet' look, they'd only clash with current style. Well, that and I have no feet soo...#$b#...I guess you can keep them. Good luck getting the stink out though!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.1": "I thought grave-snails were the most disgusting thing down here...$u#$b#You've just topped them on my gross-o-meter; bravo!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.2": "It's my birthday?! You know me so well; I love it!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.3": "Is this a birthday gift?$h#$b#Erm, well... at least you tried I suppose. Thanks anyway.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.4": "Oh wow, I've never seen tea like this before!$h#$b#Can you see the aura around it?#$b#The steam sparkles like a precious gem!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.5": "Oooo, a new book! Thanks, @.$h#$b#I can't wait to read this!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.6": "I adore malachite; it looks like sparkly velvet!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.7": "Oh, a movie sounds great!$h#$b#I'll have to manifest a disguise though; I imagine I'd scare the surface folks if I went into the town like this.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.8": "I feel weird.$u#$b#The energy of the spirits feel overwhelmingly strong today... I don't think it's malicious though.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.9": "The nature spirits are at it again.$u#$b#I can't quite tell what their intensions are... I wish I understood them better.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.10": "It's such a strange feeling.$u#$b#I don't know how I know, but I can sense that the forest spirits are grateful to you.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.11": "Oooo; a moving picture theater opened in your town.#$b#I've heard about them before but never seen one in person; it sounds like such fun!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.12": "You got married?!$u#$b#To be honest, I find romance disgusting... but I'm happy if you're happy!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.13": "I heard you got divorced; I'm sorry.$s#$b#Hey, now you'll have more free time to visit me though... I guess every cloud has a silver lining!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.14": "Congratulations on the second ride around the marriage-go-round!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.15": "Really? Divorced again? You're a real heartbreaker, eh?!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.16": "Hey, I've heard you've got crabs!$h#$b#In your pond... on the farm.#$b#Why are you looking at me like that?!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.17": "I saw that you repaired Cassandra's old cottage. She had it built so she didn't have to mix with us in the Miner's Hut...#$b#... which was great as none of us wanted that evil old hag anywhere near.$h#$b#Anyhoo, I'm sure you'll put it to good use.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.18": "I thought that lady was one of my hallucinations...#$b#I didn't mean to scare her.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.19": "I wonder what that eccentric old man was talking about.$u#$b#He seemed a few books short of a stack if you ask me.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.20": "I'm trying to practice levitating items without losing my temper... it's kinda tricky!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.21": "When Sid told me about the Speakeasy, I was hoping maybe some of the other miners would be there...#$b#... they weren't though. I feel sad that none of my old friends or my parents are still here.$s#$b#I am grateful for all of my new friends though and I'd have none of this if it wasn't for you!#$b#Your friendship means the most to me.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.22": "That was the first time I felt brave enough to approach Demetrius.#$b#I've been watching him for a while now and I'm thrilled he's going to let me join in with his study!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.23": "I've been thinking about how lonely I used to feel; I convinced myself completely that I deserved it.$s#$b#Looking back, it seems so silly, but at the time in was like being stuck in a black hole.#$b#I guess a friendly hand can do wonders... but if you're not willing or ready to climb out yourself, that hole is where you'll stay.#$b#Ah, ignore me. I'm feeling a little philosophical today!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Special.24": "You made it! It looks just like I remember.$h#$b#It really brings back happy memories; thanks for showing me.$h#$b#IUmm, as I can't eat it, I hope you don't mind if I feed it to the grave-snails later?$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.1": "I like spring. It's like watching the world around you re-awaken after a long slumber.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.2": "I like my lessons with Mr. Rasmodius, but I prefer research with Demetrius.#$b#I still find it hard to get my head around all of the magical mumbo-jumbo, whereas logic and facts are much more comforting.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.3": "I can really recommend standing outside in the springtime rain! Listening to the frogs croak and call is like a soundtrack of nature...#$b#... nature and squishy amphibian love.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.4": "Spring is the season for everyone; sunny days, crisp evenings and a good mix of crop-quenching rain!#$b#I mean, it's no Fall... but I do have a fondness for this season.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.5": "I miss the seeing the blossoms on the trees; nothing much changes in the Caverns. I might head outside later.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.6": "Wanna hear a joke about nachos?#$b#Oh, never mind... it's way too cheesy.$h#$b#Hey, I never said it was a GOOD joke!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.7": "They were building another mine before ours collapsed, though I think that one is abandoned now too.#$b#There used to be an elevator linking our mines somewhere near Cassandra's old cottage.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.8": "I hated summer when I was alive.#$b#No school, sticky heat and biting bugs... no thanks! I'm no fan of it now either, to be honest.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.9": "Do you think it's possible for ghosts to have allergies?#$b#This season makes my soul itch!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.10": "Minerals are fascinating, don't you think?!#$b#I love finding all of the intricate flaws; it's like gazing into a tiny galaxy.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.11": "$query PLAYER_VISITED_LOCATION Current Azathii.ForgottenWoods_ForgottenHill#My village used to be to the south of Pilgrimage Hill, though it's mostly overgrown and forgotten now.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.12": "Bees are amazing creatures! 85% of all flowering plants rely on them for pollination, including crops.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.13": "You know the only part of this season I really enjoy?! The storms!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.14": "I've been trying to teach Sid's bone wolf how to play catch; his jaw keeps falling off though.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.15": "Fall is the most beautiful season, so many shades of orange, red and green!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.16": "I have so many fond memories of this time of year.$h#$b#In the evenings we would sit around a crackling fire while my father told ghost stories.#$b#The irony is not lost on me.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.17": "Sometimes, I'll go out into the woods just to watch the falling leaves swirl and dance.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.18": "I don't eat or drink, obviously, but I do enjoy watching a soothing cup of tea this time of year; the steam is slightly hypnotic.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.19": "Autumnal trees make me think of a phoenix, bursting into a brightly-hued mass of flames, only to expire and be reborn anew.#$b#Nature is amazing.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.20": "$query PLAYER_VISITED_LOCATION Current Azathii.ForgottenWoods_ForgottenSmallCrypt#There's an interesting old cemetery on Pilgrimage Hill... just avoid the skeletons; they aren't as friendly as the ones in the Speakeasy",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.21": "Oh, hi @. I was just thinking about snow.#$b#It can hide every imperfection while creating a perfect sparkling wonderland... but spend too long in it and it'll freeze you to the bone.#$b#I'm sure there's a lesson to be had there.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.22": "This is a tough time of year for me. The Feast of the Winter Star is especially hard.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.23": "The anniversary of the mine collapse is coming soon.#$b#I'll spend that day in silence for my family and friends.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.24": "I'll feel so much better when the New Year begins.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Seasonal.25": "You shouldn't be here today; you should be with your family and friends.#$b#Every moment in the company of loved ones is precious.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.1": "It's a little depressing in here, but it's home...#$b#... I think?!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.2": "I remember little things about myself... I know I like to laugh.#$b#I don't think I've done it in a very long time though.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.3": "Legend says that if you throw a penny into the Catacombs fountain, you'll be blessed with luck for the whole day.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.4": "Be careful when crossing the suspension bridges; pit-fiends live in those chasms. Whatever you do, do not fall down.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.5": "I heard those giant glowing mushrooms were cultivated by some kind of religious crusaders, so they could grow crops in dark places.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.6": "The atmosphere of this place feels very dark and heavy.#$b#I think something bad happened here and I'm scared to remember what.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.7": "Oh, hi @! I was hoping you'd stop by today. I hope that farming life is going well for you.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.8": "I adore nature; especially animals.$h#$b#I have to watch them from afar though as they're all scared of me.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.9": "Pit-fiends are nasty little imp-like cretins.#$b#It's hilarious watching them try to bite me and failing spectacularly!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.10": "The dead of night is the best time to visit the surface.#$b#During all my years as a ghost I've never been seen by anyone.#$b#Animals are different though, they can always sense me and they really don't like it.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.11": "I've heard that some ghosts still look like they did when they were alive.#$b#I, however, look like someone left a wet blanket outside on a frosty night... lucky me, eh?!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.12": "Some days I struggle with the bad memories of this place.$s#$b#Your visits always cheer me up though.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.13": "I wonder if I truly enjoyed eating while I was alive; I find the whole concept of digestion strangely disgusting now.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.14": "Did you know that the animals that dwell down here are called 'Troglobites'?!#$b#They're mostly blind and are so well adapted to life down here; they'd struggle to survive on the surface.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.15": "'Galdoff's Guide to Ghostly Etiquette' is a fascinating read; I have to admit, it's pretty accurate.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.16": "Ugh, those Wild Shrines in the Hot Springs!$u#$b#Only someone who delights in frustrating others would come up with such a ridiculous idea.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.17": "$query PLAYER_VISITED_LOCATION Current Azathii.TheForgottenCaverns_ForgottenGrotto#I can always sense it when you visit the Grotto. I'm not totally sure how I do it, but I block the siren's song.#$b#You really should stay away from them though; those evil harridans scare me.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.18": "Hi @! I'm pondering over something.$u#$b#I can manifest outfits for myself, when needed, and I'm wondering if I should try manifesting hair too...$u#$b#... maybe a long flowing mane, maybe a giant green Mohawk?$h#$b#Decisions, decisions...$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.19": "I'm in awe of the stalactites in the Hot Springs.$h#$b#They're composed of calcium carbonate, but it's the presence of manganese oxide that gives them their dark-brown hue.#$b#When you look up at them, the moisture makes them sparkle like the night sky.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.20": "The glowing bugs down here are mesmerizing; they're rather eerie but quite beautiful.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.21": "I think I might take a stroll around the woods tonight; it helps to clear my head.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.22": "I'm having an existential crisis.#$b#I never used to believe in magic, only science and facts... yet here I am!$u#$b#If I had a literal brain, I think it'd be melting out of my ears about now.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.23": "I used to enjoy school. My parents wanted me to be a lawyer, but I was always more interested in natural science.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.24": "Grave-snails were in the mineshaft again last night. I enjoy watching them; they're equal parts disgusting and fascinating.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.25": "Have you met Earl? He's the chef in the Speakeasy.#$b#If you want some solid advice, do NOT drink anything he gives you! I think I saw toenail clippings in one of his potions *gag*.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.26": "I think I might read something new tonight.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.27": "$query PLAYER_VISITED_LOCATION Current Azathii.ForgottenWoods_ForgottenShrine#The old forest spirit shrine makes me feel sad; they were crumbling ruins even back when I was alive.$s",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.28": "Petra seems nice; she reminds me of my old school headmistress.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.29": "I enjoyed performing my own experiments when I was alive.#$b#I remember I hid slices of bread around our house to establish what the best conditions for mold-growth were.#$b#I named the furriest slice 'George'...$h#$b#... my mother was NOT happy when she found him.$u ",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.30": "Ugh, I really want to play Junimo Kart, but the completionist in me is preventing it until I finally conquer Journey of the Prairie King.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.31": "I'd like to think of myself as an impartial observer to all nature...#$b#... but dear Yoba, those Fangtooth fish in the catacombs are UGLY!$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.32": "Someone in the Speakeasy was talking about the Catacomb blooms last night.#$b#They said that glovewort strengthens us undead and that touching the violets calls evil spirits to chase you down.#$b#Personally I think they'd had waaay too many of Earl's potions to drink.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.33": "Visiting the old Orchard is rather theraputic for me now.$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.34": "Why are ghosts good cheerleaders?#$b#Because they have a lot of spirit!$h#$b#Sorry, Dave has been teaching me some of his jokes in the Speakeasy$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.35": "I think it's impossible to beat Journey of the Prairie King!$s#$b#I can't get past the Graveyard... and no, I'm not being ironic.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.36": "Demetrius has given me so many books on natural science to read, it's really hard to choose which one to read first!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.37": "Sid threw that sketchy grave-robber into the pit-fiends chasm last night; it was HILARIOUS!$h",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.38": "Hi @, hope the day is treating you well!",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.39": "Don't tell Sid, but I much prefer the Ghastly Games Room to the Speakeasy.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.40": "I think I might visit the Hot Springs island tonight.",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.41": "Dave told me that ghosts can catch grave-mites.#$b#I know he's just trying to prank me... but I kinda feel itchy thinking about it.$u",
  "Dialogue_Bob.Weekly.42": "I tried watching the flight patterns of some fireflies last night.#$b#It was great at first, but then I just felt dizzy.$u",

//BOB EVENTS
  "Event_Bob.Intro.1": "Huh? Oh great; another hallucination.$u#$b#The last one I had here was a weird purple cat-monkey with sunglasses; he was funny.$h",
  "Event_Bob.Intro.2Q": "So how long are you going to taunt me for?",  
  "Event_Bob.Intro.2A1": "I'm not here to taunt you; I'm real!",
  "Event_Bob.Intro.2A2": "Well, I was thinking a week or two, then I'm moving on to terrorize a rather heartless conglomerate CEO.",
  "Event_Bob.Intro.3": "Hmm, I'm not completely convinced... but I guess I'll trust you.$u#$b#My name is... ummm... I can't remember.#$b# It's been so long. Ummm...$u#$b#Bob! Ha! That's it; my name is Bob. Nice to meet you!$h",
  "Event_Bob.Intro.4": "Wait a minute, my hallucinations aren't usually quippy...$u#$b#YOU'RE REAL!!$h#$b#My name is... ummm... I can't remember.#$b# It's been so long. Ummm...$u#$b#Bob! Ha! That's it; my name is Bob. It's nice to meet you!$h",
  "Event_Bob.Intro.5": "I know it's not the most comfortable place...$s#$b#... but if you wanted to stop by again sometime and say 'hello' that would be nice.$h", 
  "Event_Bob.1Heart.1": "Oh, Hi @. Sorry, I was just a little lost in thought.#$b#My memories have started to return and I... I'm having a hard time with them.$s",
  "Event_Bob.1Heart.2": "I've been drifting away into darkness for a while now; each time it's like it takes pieces of me away.$s",
  "Event_Bob.1Heart.3": "I remember that I like nature and I love my parents, but I can't remember what I'm doing here.$s",
  "Event_Bob.1Heart.4": "Ugh, I'm sorry. I'm sure you didn't come here to watch me wallow in self-pity.$s#$b#How about you tell me what's happening on your farm for a while, I'm sure that'll cheer me up.$h",
  "Event_Bob.2Heart.1": "My memories have mostly come back now.#$b#My father worked here... until he got sick.$s",
  "Event_Bob.2Heart.2": "The mine supervisor, Cassandra, visited me at school and threatened to stop my father's sick pay unless I came here and worked in his place.#$b#I knew my parents would never allow it, so I...#$b#... I lied to them. I told them I was going to school, but came here instead. I knew we needed the money.$s", 
  "Event_Bob.2Heart.3": "The miners took really good care of me though. I worked here for three months before...#$b#... before it happened.$s",
  "Event_Bob.2Heart.4": "We all told Cassandra the beams in the mineshaft needed repairing, but she ignored us.$s#$b#I can remember the day quite vividly now; she came down here, spewing out one of her usual tirades, and the earthquake hit... and...$u",
  "Event_Bob.2Heart.5Q": "... and we were gone. I was 15...",
  "Event_Bob.2Heart.5A1": "Oh Bob, I'm so sorry.",
  "Event_Bob.2Heart.5A2": "Hey, look on the bright side; now you've got nifty ghost powers and haunting people could be so much fun!",
  "Event_Bob.2Heart.6": "It's okay.$s#$b#Please keep coming to see me. I know it doesn't sound like it now, but our chats make me feel better.",
  "Event_Bob.2Heart.7": "You weren't blessed with tact, were you?!$u#$b#Actually, that was pretty funny. Thanks for trying to lighten the mood, @!$h",
  "Event_Bob.3Heart.1.Wizard": "The fates are sometimes cruel... yet your spirit burns all the brighter for it.",
  "Event_Bob.3Heart.2.Wizard": "I have seen variations of your path ahead, each as difficult as the next.#$b#Persevere and we shall meet again soon. ",
  "Event_Bob.3Heart.3": "...?$u",
  "Event_Bob.3Heart.4.Wizard": "Greetings, @. I was summoned here by the potent spirit force emanating from the young fellow over there.",
  "Event_Bob.3Heart.5.Wizard": "He is upon a great precipice; an ill-timed move will see him plunged into darkness...#$b#... yet, a comforting hand may retrieve him from the brink. ",
  "Event_Bob.3Heart.6.Wizard": "There would be dire consequences if I were to influence his decision.#$b#I have seen that your fates are entwined so, until he chooses his path, I must entrust his care to you.#$b#Farewell.",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.1": "Oh, hello @.#$b#I've been staring at this epitaph for hours; I can't seem to pull myself away.$s",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.2": "Every time I read it I...#$b#... I get angrier. It's an outright LIE!$a",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.3": "Nobody is by me, I'm alone! I miss my parents so much that it hurts. I... I can't find them anywhere!$s",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.4Q": "They must have moved on and left me, just like all of the other miners.",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.4A1": "You're not alone, Bob. I'm here by your side.",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.4A2": "Don't keep your emotions bottled up. You need to let it out; shout, scream!",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.5": "NO! You don't understand! IT'S NOT FAIR!$a",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.6": "AAAHHHHHHHH! IT'S NOT FAIR!$a",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.7": "I'm moving the rock??!$u#$b#I'M MOVING THE ROCK!$h",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.8": "I haven't moved anything since I died; I didn't think I could!$u#$b#I can MOVE things.$h#$b#It... it's been so hard to just exist and have no effect on anything around me.",
  "Event_Bob.4Heart.9": "I can't believe this has happened!$h#$b#I should probably head back home now. Um, @...#$b#... I don't know what I'd have done if you weren't here...$s#$b#Thank you.$h",
  "Event_Bob.NewFriends.1": "Oh wow, hi @! You know about this place too?!$h#$b#Sid came to see me after my little meltdown in the Catacombs.#$b#I can't believe I'd made a barrier to keep everyone away.$u",
  "Event_Bob.NewFriends.2": "Everyone is so nice to me here.#$b#They've been wanting to meet me for over a century! Can you believe that?!$h",
  "Event_Bob.NewFriends.3": "I don't know how you managed to get through my barrier when no one else could...$u#$b#... but I'm so glad you did.$h",
  "Event_Bob.NewFriends.4": "I going to head home now; I want to see if I can lift one of those big boulders next!$h#$b#See you soon, @!",
  "Event_Bob.5Heart.1.Wizard": "Focus. Control your mind.#$b#Feel the threads of reality, gather them around you and use them to do your will.",
  "Event_Bob.5Heart.2": "What threads? I don't see any threads!$u#$b#I want the book to move and it's moving.",
  "Event_Bob.5Heart.3.Wizard": "You will not improve until you cast aside the chains of logic and open your mind.",
  "Event_Bob.5Heart.4.Wizard": "That's enough for today.#$b#Continue to practice until our next lesson and I expect you to have read the book within that time too.#$b#Your mind needs exercising in more ways than one.",
  "Event_Bob.5Heart.5": "Yes, Sir.",
  "Event_Bob.5Heart.6": "Ugh, he's stricter than my grandma!$u#$b#I am getting a lot better though and I quite enjoy his lessons!$h",
  "Event_Bob.5Heart.7": "I think I might actually be strong enough now to do a little tidying in here...$u#$b#... but I'm going to need some help...$h",
  "Event_Bob.6Heart.1": "I'm so sorry! I didn't mean to scare you.$s#$b#I just wondered what notes you were taking?$u",
  "Event_Bob.6Heart.2.Demetrius": "I wasn't scared; you just surprised me a little, that's all.$h",
  "Event_Bob.6Heart.3.Demetrius": "I was recording my musings on these mushrooms; the reaction of the luciferase and luciferin is extraordinary in these specimens.",
  "Event_Bob.6Heart.4": "You're talking about the bioluminescence, right?!$h#$b#I read that rotting wood is needed to cause that reaction in mushrooms... but there's none here.",
  "Event_Bob.6Heart.5.Demetrius": "Yes, that's correct.$h#$b#I've taken a few samples for analysis and I'm hoping to discover some answers back in my lab.",
  "Event_Bob.6Heart.6": "Umm... if you come back, would you mind if I join you again?#$b#I'd really like to learn more about these mushrooms.$h",
  "Event_Bob.6Heart.7.Demetrius": "I don't see why not.#$b#I'll definitely be coming back soon; these Caverns are a naturalistic wonder and two curious minds are always better than one!$h",
  "Event_Bob.6Heart.8": "Great! My name is Bob, by the way.$h",
  "Event_Bob.6Heart.9.Demetrius": "Well, it has been a pleasure to meet you, Bob. My name is Demetrius.$h#$b#I'll look forward to our next research venture.",
  "Event_Bob.7Heart.1": "Oh hi @! I hope you don't mind me being here.",
  "Event_Bob.7Heart.2": "This used to be Cassandra's orchard. She never let any of us miners in here... but we would sneak in anyway.",
  "Event_Bob.7Heart.3": "The fruit she grew was amazing, though she never shared them with us willingly.#$b#After spending all day in the dark, biting into a piece was like an explosion of sunshine in your mouth!$h#$b#It's something to do with the giant mushrooms in the Caverns I think.$u",
  "Event_Bob.7Heart.4": "The last time I was here, I was alive. I've been avoiding this place because of how much I hated her.",
  "Event_Bob.7Heart.5": "I thought this would be painful, but do you know what?! It isn't.$u#$b#I just have happy memories of being here with the other miners.#$b#Annie, one of the older miners, would holler a grizzly cry of 'Scrumping for Justice!' every time we stole some fruit.#$b#I still have no idea what she meant, but it made me laugh all the same.$h",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.1": "Oh no, no, NO! Ahhh!$u",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.2": "Hi, @! I just died again...#u#$b#... in the game; not literally.$u",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.3": "I never thought I'd have this much fun ever again.$h#$b#It's an incredibly frustrating kind of fun though.$u",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.4Q": "Which game do you like the most?",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.4A1": "Journey of the Prairie King.", 
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.4A2": "Junimo Kart.",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.4A3": "Slot machines.",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.5": "Me too! It's challenging... but really fun.$h",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.6": "I haven't played that yet, but I'm looking forward to it.#$b#I'm trying to complete Journey of the Prairie King first.",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.7": "They're not really my cup of tea. I find it a little boring just pulling a lever over and over again.$u",
  "Event_Bob.8Heart.8": "You know what?! I don't think it matters what we play, but it's definitely more fun doing it alongside friends.$h",  
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.1": "I still keep dropping things.$s#$b#As soon as I start questioning what I'm doing and how I'm doing it, I lose control.",
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.2.Wizard": "The truth of reality exceeds far beyond logic; to doubt this is to doubt yourself.#$b#It will all become easier with time... but only if you apply yourself.",
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.3": "...$s",  
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.4.Wizard": "I shall send over a few more books which may help.#$b#You should find the volumes of Yalenfydd's 'Realms of the Opaque' rather enlightening, but do take better care of them.",
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.5.Wizard": "I did not appreciate scraping grave-snail slime from the last tome you borrowed, no matter how good an alchemical reagent it may be.",
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.6": "Hehe, yeah, sorry about that. I won't let it happen again, I promise.$h",
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.7.Wizard": "See that you don't.#$b#Now, there's no time for idle chatter; you have reading to do.",
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.8": "Yes, Sir.",
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.9": "Hi, @! I didn't know you were here.$h#$b#Ugh, I'd better be off before he finds more for me to do.$u#$b# See you soon!",
  "Event_Bob.9Heart.10.Wizard": "That boy may be the key to unlocking many unknown mysteries.#$b#Now, if you'll excuse me, I have new lesson plans to construct.",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.1": "Oh, hey @.",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.2": "I was just cleaning up the headstone and laying some fresh flowers.#$b#I'm so glad I was able to give them a proper burial.",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.3": "I never really had any friends at school; I was too busy with my studies.$s#$b#I knew some of the workers here through my father, but I still remember feeling intimidated on my first day...",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.4": "... they made me feel so welcome though.$h#$b#Men and women of all ages who became like a second family to me. None of us deserved this.$s#$b#I hope they're at rest now.",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.5": "Oh, I almost forgot! I've got something I want you to have.",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.6": "It isn't much; it's just an old family recipe I wanted you to have. My...#$b#... my mother used to love this.$s#$b#It's my father's recipe; he used to bake it for us every Sunday.",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.7": "I just wanted to thank you in some way.",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.8": "I can't help but marvel at everything I've accomplished since I met you.",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.9": "This place was my tomb for so long and now it's a home that I love.$h#$b#I have friends again... and hobbies... and lessons! I have a life again and it's all thanks to you.$h",
  "Event_Bob.10Heart.10": "I... umm...$s#$b#... I'm grateful to call you my friend.#$b#I just wanted you to know that.$h",
  "Event_Bob.1WoodsBonus.1": "I wasn't expecting anyone to be here... I thought this place was long abandoned.",
  "Event_Bob.1WoodsBonus.2": "This is where my parents remains were buried... a forgotten grave in a dark corner.$s#$b#I thought about finding a nice place to re-bury them, but it felt wrong to disturb their bones.",
  "Event_Bob.1WoodsBonus.3": "Sid made me a headstone and helped me to bury my bones next to theirs.$s#$b#I miss them so much, but I suppose I feel a little better knowing that some part of me is with them again.",
  "Event_Bob.1WoodsBonus.4": "I hope they're not mad at me and that they're happy, wherever they are.$s",
  "Event_Bob.1WoodsBonus.5": "Sorry, I think I need a little time alone.$s",
  "Event_Bob.2WoodsBonus.1": "Hi, @!#$b#It's beautiful up here, isn't it?!$h",
  "Event_Bob.2WoodsBonus.2": "I used to come here every Sunday afternoon with my parents.#$b#In the warmer seasons we'd have picnics and in the cooler ones we'd have campfires and tell stories.$h",  
  "Event_Bob.2WoodsBonus.3": "Good memories of them still hurt, but remembering them keeps them with me...$s#$b#... by my side.$s",
  "Event_Bob.2WoodsBonus.4": "I suppose the epitaph in the Catacombs was right... in a way.$u#$b#I just needed some time and a good friend to help me see it.$h"
}
